block.original:
``Skiljumk heilir!munat sko~pum vinna;

nu hefr, Gri`pir! velgo~rt sem beiddak;

fljo`tt myndir þu`fri`þri segja

mi`na a_e`vi,ef ma_e`ttir þat.''

block.translation:
``Now fare thee well!our fates we shun not;

And well has Gripiranswered my wish;

More of joyto me wouldst tell

Of my life to comeif so thou couldst.''
